text: La Notte (; ) is a 1961 Italian French drama movie directed by Michelangelo Antonioni and starring Marcello Mastroianni, Jeanne Moreau, Monica Vitti, Bernhard Wicki, Rosy Mazzacurati. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1961 drama movies Category:Italian drama movies Category:French drama movies Category:Movies directed by Michelangelo Antonioni
